<section class="page-hero"><div class="sh-container"><div class="sh-eyebrow">Our Story</div><h1 class="sh-h1">Shadeless is not about changing your skin tone.</h1><p class="sh-body">It is about helping skin look clearer, smoother, more even, and more refined — in every skin tone.</p></div></section>
<section class="sh-section"><div class="sh-container sh-grid sh-grid-2"><div><h2 class="sh-h2">Less visual shadow. More visible clarity.</h2><p class="sh-body">The name Shadeless is built around the idea of reducing the look of visual unevenness: dullness, rough texture, visible marks, and lack of clarity that can make skin appear tired or inconsistent.</p><p class="sh-body"><strong>It is not about whitening. It is not about bleaching. It is not about making skin lighter.</strong></p></div><div class="sh-card sh-card-soft"><h3 class="sh-h3">Why we exist</h3><p>Many people own multiple serums but still feel their routine is incomplete. Shadeless was created to organize advanced skincare into three clear steps: Prepare, Optimize, Enhance.</p></div></div></section>
